<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 21:11:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日本海上保安厅称，朝鲜计划于5月27日至6月4日期间发射卫星火箭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-plans-launch-satellite-rocket-between-may-27-june-4-japan-coast-2024-05-26/</link><description>日本海上保安厅周一表示，朝鲜已通知日本，计划于 5 月 27 日至 6 月 4 日期间向黄海和吕宋岛以东发射一枚运载太空卫星的火箭。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 19:06:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-plans-launch-satellite-rocket-between-may-27-june-4-japan-coast-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>官员称巴基斯坦逮捕了11名参与杀害中国工程师的武装分子</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-arrests-11-militants-involved-chinese-engineers-killing-say-officials-2024-05-26/</link><description>官员周日表示，巴基斯坦当局逮捕了 11 名伊斯兰激进分子，他们参与了 3 月份在该国北部与阿富汗接壤的自杀式爆炸事件，导致 5 名中国工程师死亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-arrests-11-militants-involved-chinese-engineers-killing-say-officials-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员本周访问台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-visiting-taiwan-this-week-2024-05-26/</link><description>事实上的美国大使馆周日表示，由众议院外交事务委员会主席迈克尔·麦考尔率领的美国议员代表团本周将访问台湾。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 11:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-visiting-taiwan-this-week-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>李强总理表示鼓励三星加大对华投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/samsung-encouraged-invest-more-china-premier-li-qiang-says-2024-05-26/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，中国总理李强周日对三星董事长李在镕表示，中国欢迎这家韩国企业集团进一步投资，因为中国市场的外国企业正在努力应对地缘政治的不确定性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 11:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/samsung-encouraged-invest-more-china-premier-li-qiang-says-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>来自饱受蹂躏的哈尔科夫的泽伦斯基敦促拜登和习近平参加和平峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/zelenskiy-kharkiv-urges-biden-xi-join-peace-summit-2024-05-26/</link><description>目前尚不清楚拜登或任何来自中国的人是否会出席。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 08:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/zelenskiy-kharkiv-urges-biden-xi-join-peace-summit-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>与中国前线的台湾酒吧将历史融入鸡尾酒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-bar-frontline-with-china-blends-history-into-cocktails-2024-05-26/</link><description>在距离中国厦门和泉州不到一小时船程的台湾金门，酒吧老板 Powei Lee 将这个小岛的战争恐惧的过去融入鸡尾酒中，吸引了大批人群。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 04:26:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-bar-frontline-with-china-blends-history-into-cocktails-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国与美国盟友韩国、日本讨论安全和商业问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-li-lands-seoul-trilateral-summit-with-south-korea-japan-2024-05-26/</link><description>中国国务院总理李强周日与韩国总统尹锡烈同意启动外交安全对话并恢复自由贸易谈判，并与日本首相岸田文雄讨论了台湾地区的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-li-lands-seoul-trilateral-summit-with-south-korea-japan-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统在中国演习后表达善意，美国议员抵达</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/after-china-drills-taiwan-president-again-offers-talks-2024-05-26/</link><description>中国多次痛斥赖清德为“分裂分子”，并拒绝了他的会谈提议。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:10:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/after-china-drills-taiwan-president-again-offers-talks-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾日益政治化的变装皇后在主场令粉丝惊叹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-increasingly-political-drag-race-queen-wows-fans-home-stage-2024-05-26/</link><description>台湾选手 Nymphia Wind 是第一个在鲁保罗变装皇后秀中夺得桂冠的东亚人，也是一个日益政治化的人物，她在台北举行的大型返校演出中让数百名粉丝惊叹不已。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 01:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-increasingly-political-drag-race-queen-wows-fans-home-stage-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜指责美国和韩国飞行间谍飞机和船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-accuses-us-south-korea-flying-spy-planes-ships-2024-05-25/</link><description>官方媒体朝中社周日称，朝鲜国防部指责美国和韩国加强朝韩边境周围的侦察活动，并警告称，如果朝鲜主权和安全受到侵犯，朝鲜将采取行动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 22:36:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-accuses-us-south-korea-flying-spy-planes-ships-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>意大利部长表示欧盟应效仿美国对中国商品征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-should-follow-us-tariffs-over-chinese-goods-italy-minister-says-2024-05-25/</link><description>意大利工业部长阿道夫·乌尔索周六表示，欧盟应效仿美国，通过对中国产品征收关税来保护其工业。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 16:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-should-follow-us-tariffs-over-chinese-goods-italy-minister-says-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦表示，在俄罗斯的欧洲银行面临“巨大风险”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/european-banks-russia-face-awful-lot-risk-yellen-says-2024-05-25/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦告诉路透社，欧洲银行在俄罗斯经营面临着越来越大的风险，美国正在考虑加强对被发现为俄罗斯战争活动提供交易援助的银行的二级制裁。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 15:31:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/european-banks-russia-face-awful-lot-risk-yellen-says-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>美国国务院表示，美国对中国在台湾海峡的军事演习“深感关切”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-deeply-concerned-over-china-military-drills-taiwan-strait-state-dept-says-2024-05-25/</link><description>北京表示，这些演习是对台湾新总统周一就职演说的“惩罚”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 15:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-deeply-concerned-over-china-military-drills-taiwan-strait-state-dept-says-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行行长帕内塔表示，对于降息必要性的共识日益增强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecbs-panetta-says-consensus-growing-need-rate-cut-2024-05-25/</link><description>欧洲央行政策制定者法比奥·帕内塔周六表示，随着通胀减弱，欧洲央行内部越来越多地认为有必要首次降息，为放松货币政策创造条件。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 14:10:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecbs-panetta-says-consensus-growing-need-rate-cut-2024-05-25/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦表示乌克兰贷款计划得到支持，但还需要做更多工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-says-ukraine-loan-plan-has-support-more-work-needed-2024-05-25/</link><description>该计划将探索如何利用约 3000 亿美元俄罗斯冻结资产的未来收入来帮助乌克兰。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 13:47:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-says-ukraine-loan-plan-has-support-more-work-needed-2024-05-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>